      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage since the day I bought it. It\u2019s in truly pristine shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I'm only selling because I need the space, but I know you're going to love it as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
