    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since the day it was driven off the lot. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-fresh luster, free of any swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, reflecting a life spent in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the premium leather still carries that distinct new-car scent, with no creases on the bolsters or wear on the touchpoints. All electronics and mechanical systems function flawlessly, supported by a meticulous service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. From the pristine engine bay to the spotless undercarriage, this car represents the pinnacle of its class. It is, quite simply, the finest example currently available on the market for a discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
